    "id": "kpop-cafes-theme-stores-hongdae-myeongdong-2025",
    "title": "Best K-pop Cafes and Theme Stores in Hongdae and Myeongdong",
    "excerpt": "Explore Seoul’s best K-pop cafés and theme stores in Hongdae and Myeongdong — from BTS cafés to BT21 stores, where fans can experience Korea’s idol culture up close in 2025.",
    "date": "Oct 23, 2025",
    "dateIso": "2025-10-23",
