    "id": "hidden-gems-in-korea-beyond-seoul-2025",
    "title": "Hidden Gems in Korea Beyond Seoul (Underrated Travel Spots)",
    "excerpt": "Discover Korea’s hidden gems beyond Seoul — from Jecheon’s healing lakes and Hadong’s tea fields to Tongyeong’s seaside charm and Ulleungdo’s mysterious cliffs. A 2025 guide to Korea’s underrated travel spots.",
